title: 1 Parking Space - Storage Room  -  Private Patio
posting_body: ['2 Bedrooms, 1 Bathroom, kitchen, dishwasher, disposal, living room-dining room combo.', 'The oversized living room-dining room opens with sliding doors to a private patio and common garden area.', 'Both bedrooms are large with ample storage/closets spaces.', 'The master bedroom features a wall length closet.', 'Includes 1 parking space and private storage room.', 'There is also a common laundry room.', 'This condo is part of a 17-unit condominium association at the end of Newman Road that borders the Malden Greenway walking trail.', 'The property features mature trees, and a private parking area.', 'It is professionally managed, including landscaping, snow removal, and weekly common area maintenance.', '1 Queen Size Bed, 2 twin beds and a 48" flat screen tv in unit, if needed.', 'Available August 1st, 2022.', "Terms: First Month Rent, Security Deposit, Half Month Broker's Fee. 1 year fixed-term lease with option to renew.", 'For viewing, contact First Estate Realty: (857)928-5557.']
